{"tid":1553792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日正式踏入運動第三個月","createTime":"2019-09-08T17:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T18:05:03.000Z","uid":84408,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61f176b6920b6301987a5a05fee2740a02977da3","tid":1553792,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:17:24.000Z","msg":"大家過得好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由6月到今日一切真係好似發緊一場夢咁<br />\n由8月開始 每晚周圍都有唔同嘅事發生<br />\n有手足離世 有手足被捕 有手足被虐<br />\n資訊疲勞 發夢發到攰嘅大家記得要多休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地呢一個係長期抗戰<br />\n如果每一日都精神緊繃 好快就係到我地癲先<br />\n無論輸定贏 最後大家都會響度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個都不能小<br />\n係咪啊!!!<br />\n[size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span>[size=6]"},{"pid":"90a06a1c7e63e476fa0d013a6f1331637907442e","tid":1553792,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:22:07.000Z","msg":"有人就餓死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《急推》 前線唔好餓死呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64ae4fe6d65e29391fb2b474c0e5d65098e31309","tid":1553792,"uid":313054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"樓主錫返啖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa8da989b7148a6f64c7f03e624c2aee2481c97","tid":1553792,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"手足比人拉，點會好<br />\n<br />\nPS<br />\n勇武走得太前，後勤補給不足，文宣唔夠人！<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，免費港鐵；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Br9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=e72fd81d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 低消費，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"6afc33fe967e67bdc57b2cd553ebd8fee9ecd12f","tid":1553792,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:47:46.000Z","msg":"因為呢3個月冇左條女"},{"pid":"7a2689076cdc0c05470f5c988428b356b463d9c7","tid":1553792,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6afc33fe967e67bdc57b2cd553ebd8fee9ecd12f","tid":1553792,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:47:46.000Z","msg":"因為呢3個月冇左條女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:50:40.000Z","msg":"巴打要堅信自己做嘅事<br />\n係咪好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727bd947344770a40ed84602723cbbee2bb66efd","tid":1553792,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaa8da989b7148a6f64c7f03e624c2aee2481c97","tid":1553792,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"手足比人拉，點會好<br />\n<br />\nPS<br />\n勇武走得太前，後勤補給不足，文宣唔夠人！<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"h